Reviews.reviewInput: Best run of my life. Can't believe this was located only 15 miles from my house!
This was one of those trails that's just all around pleasant.
I think the Armistead location used to be an old civil war site. I was hoping to see more memorials there but only one or two historical markers.
WOD did not disappoint!!! Definitely one of my favorites in this area and I can't wait to come back!!
I ran this one with my boyfriend and we both thought it was a wonderful trail!!
Got a great run in today here, amazing place!
